          <fieldcaption>Thank you page URL</fieldcaption>
          <fielddescription>
<![CDATA[
The URL of a page where the system redirects your customers after successful purchase. It is usually a page where you say Thank you.
Note that if you use PayPal as your payment gateway, you need to configure this redirect in Configuration -> Settings -> E-commerce -> Payment gateways -> PayPal.
]]>
